OL,3,CBoys ,12 and 13, in hospital with
OL,4,Cserious injuries after scrambler bike
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,FTwo boys aged 12 and 13 remain in
OL,8,Fhospital with serious injuries
OL,9,Ffollowing a crash between a scrambler
OL,10,Fbike and a car.
OL,12,FMerseyside Police said officers were
OL,13,Fcalled to Longview Drive in Huyton at
OL,14,Faround 5.25 pm on 31 January, to
OL,15,Freports of a crash.
OL,17,FThe force said a scrambler bike with
OL,18,Ftwo schoolboy riders, aged 12 and 13,
OL,19,Fhad crashed with a bronze-coloured
OL,20,FPeugeot 3008.
