OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,FThe children were taken to the
OL,8,Fhospital for treatment of serious leg
OL,9,Finjuries, where their condition is
OL,10,Fdescribed as serious but stable.
OL,12,FTheir injuries are not believed to be
OL,13,Flife-threatening.
OL,15,FPolice have said the driver of the
OL,16,FPeugeot was not arrested but remained
OL,17,Fat the scene to assist with enquiries.
