OL,7,FLongview Drive was cordoned off
OL,8,Fbetween Hurst Park Drive and York Road
OL,9,Fto allow for emergency services to
OL,10,Fattend.
OL,12,FThe road was reopened for drivers
OL,13,Fshortly before 9.30pm.
OL,15,FChief Inspector Tom Welch said "This
OL,16,Fwas a serious collision that has left
OL,17,Ftwo young males needing treatment in
OL,18,Fhospital.
