OL,7,FThe force added: "Our teams will
OL,8,Fcontinue to proactively act on
OL,9,Finformation which identifies the
OL,10,Fillegal use of such bikes, and we have
OL,11,Fa range of tactics at our disposal to
OL,12,Ftrack and locate them.
OL,14,F"Any information you hold about them
OL,15,Fbeing ridden antisocially will help us
OL,16,Fnot only prevent them from causing a
OL,17,Fmenace in our communities, but protect
OL,18,Fall road users including those riding
OL,19,Fthese bikes.
